## Quick Install

```bash
# Install Task
curl -sL https://taskfile.dev/install.sh | sh

# Copy taskfile(s) to your project
mkdir -p .taskfiles
cp -r /path/to/taskfiles/* .taskfiles/

# Include in your Taskfile.yml
includes:
  python3:
    taskfile: .taskfiles/python3/Taskfile.yml
    optional: true
```

